                <p>In Switzerland, "unemployment" (ALV/AC unemployment insurance) is a very useful system, but <strong>demanding</strong>. It's not just about "signing up": it's based on documentation, deadlines, and a demonstrable job search. Furthermore, there are two different actors and it is important to understand them from day one:</p>
