                <p>The RAV controls that you fulfill obligations: applications, availability, interviews and measures (courses, programs, internships). The cashier verifies the right and makes the payment. You can be registered in the RAV and, at the same time, have the payment blocked if documents are missing or if there are sanctions.</p>

